  "thinking": {
    "_comment": "Per-model thinking/reasoning mode configuration. When set, the proxy injects the thinking parameter into upstream requests for models that support it (DeepSeek V4 via /anthropic endpoint, etc.). type: 'enabled' enables extended thinking. budget_tokens: how many tokens the model can spend on internal reasoning (higher = deeper reasoning but slower/$$$).",
